{"tid":1775194,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"想問咁多個冷氣軍師，係咪全港嘅人都睇連登？","createTime":"2019-12-08T16:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T16:51:29.000Z","uid":199769,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c45da431b95cb5ef3cd9dc8e251b048bdefcf367","tid":1775194,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"今晚開始吹風話聽日要升級。認真講句，係咪全港嘅人都睇連登？又係習慣唔脫離同溫層。<br />\n<br />\n先唔講黎明行動仲有冇用，大三罷未搞好哂工會。<br />\n<br />\n講咗好多次，要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>脫離同溫層</strong></span>。唔係全港嘅人都睇連登。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">垃圾政府冇回應訴求行動升級，無問題。但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日一定要開記招，再開花。</span></strong></span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"793b13f20ef1d02a0c777ef45667644de4a2e6c7","tid":1775194,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:36:00.000Z","msg":"推10次冇人理就算9數"},{"pid":"04434fadf47a9eafa4548674c32e2e8a24dc0d0e","tid":1775194,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:36:28.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"d703758d86dce77a972e8cc94cbd4ae4bcd07297","tid":1775194,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:36:44.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"d263ee3daaaef2e5b06c7185f98615fc86ff5ec6","tid":1775194,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:36:57.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"e1502cc8216ed9b8822c03450e2b21d26e3a467d","tid":1775194,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:37:16.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"4b2499d23c3d5beaf5bb90560ccd8533980e634d","tid":1775194,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:37:31.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"242257cafcd1977879790502e36da473f628b4e8","tid":1775194,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:37:48.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"4057e7a3b4881a8e44132291e51d4e5386